> Node is installed 
    : node --version
> Using npm
    : npm --version
> Install Typescript
    : npm install -g typescript

> Verify typescript
    : tsc --version

> Generate a JavaScript file from this TypeScript file by:
    : tsc hello_typescript.ts

> execute this JavaScript using Node with the following command:
    : node hello_typescript.js
> the tsc command-line compiler to generate a tsconfig.json
    : tsc --init

> To compile again the tsconfig.json just run 
    > tsc
>  watch an entire directory tree, if a file changes, it will automatically recompile the entire project
    > tsc -w 